    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone seeking basic transportation at a great value. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but it remains an appealing opportunity for someone who appreciates straightforward pricing and room to make it their own. Priced to move and well suited for project-minded shoppers.",
