    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car is a straightforward, honest budget option that still has plenty to offer for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a project to tinker with. It shows its age and isn\u2019t pretending to be perfect, but it starts, drives, and gives you a lot of value for the money. A great chance to grab a cheap runabout from a seller who believes in being upfront and easy to deal with.",
