      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for someone looking for budget-friendly transportation or a project with potential. It offers strong value at this price point and is being presented as an economical choice for buyers who want a low-cost way into ownership. A sensible option for commuting, spare use, or improvement over time.",
